                    "body": "Hi [~mcolosimo-p4], I believe you're looking for\r\n{code:java}\r\noptions(arrow.int64_downcast = FALSE) {code}\r\nwhich tells {{as_vector()}} to return an {{integer64}} vector.\r\n\r\nWhen you set the option to {{FALSE}}, does that solve it for you?",
